"{\"uid\": \"aljazeera.com-gallery-2024-7-12-a-12-year-old-boxing-champ-in-mongolia-dreams-of-olympics-glory\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"In Pictures  Mongolians have won Olympic medals in boxing and other individual sports such as wrestling and archery in the past.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 128, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13, \"end\": 23, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9995468742032393, \"rank\": 0.0004531051138975155, \"text\": \"Mongolians\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Save  Share  Gerelt-Od Kherlen, 12, could not contain his excitement after winning a bronze medal in the children's national boxing championship in Mongolia.\", \"from\": 130, \"to\": 287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 278, \"end\": 286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.999999999972033, \"rank\": 2.1676550493231403e-11, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In September, his father heard about the opening of the Mongolian Boxing Academy close to their home in Dambadarjaa, a tent-dotted district on the outskirts of the capital, Ulaanbaatar.\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 345, \"end\": 354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.979405008150902, \"rank\": 0.020877524352416205, \"text\": \"Mongolian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}, {\"begin\": 355, \"end\": 361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"score\": 0.9999997815077916, \"rank\": 2.183870138861299e-07, \"text\": \"Boxing\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\"}, {\"begin\": 462, \"end\": 473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulaanbaatar\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 3.1134005316269386e-13, \"text\": \"Ulaanbaatar\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulaanbaatar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulaanbaatar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The boy had been restless.\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 501, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are happy that our son has found his passion and hobby,\\\" said his mother, Narantsetseg Narantsogt.\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 605, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He had been playing chess at school, but the programme was discontinued, she said.\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 688, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They decided to send him to the new boxing school \\\"because it will keep him away from playing on the smartphone and watching too much TV at home\\\".\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 836, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mongolia is the land of 13th century conqueror Genghis Khan, who built one of the largest empires in the world, and contact sports are part of a warrior tradition.\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 1001, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 838, \"end\": 846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.999999999972033, \"rank\": 2.1676550493231403e-11, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}, {\"begin\": 885, \"end\": 897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Genghis_Khan\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 7.435727809065241e-13, \"text\": \"Genghis Khan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Genghis_Khan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Genghis_Khan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mongolians have won Olympic medals in boxing and other individual sports such as wrestling and archery.\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1106, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1003, \"end\": 1013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9995468742032393, \"rank\": 0.0004531051138975155, \"text\": \"Mongolians\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gerelt-Od was already strong.\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1137, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Growing up in a district without running water, he fetched water every day for his family.\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1228, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He also chopped firewood, which he said helped him develop patience and resilience.\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1312, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The boxing academy taught him and dozens of other children how to punch and avoid being hit.\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1406, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gerelt-Od trained for more than two hours every day before going to school.\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1482, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Less than a year later, he was among more than 400 boxers between the ages of 10 and 14 in the national championship.\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1601, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His third-place finish in the 10- to 12-year old, 32kg (70lb) weight category surprised his family.\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1701, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He now wears a T-shirt with pictures of famous Mongolian boxers and dreams of becoming an Olympic champion.\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1810, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1750, \"end\": 1759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.979405008150902, \"rank\": 0.020877524352416205, \"text\": \"Mongolian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Al Jazeera English:\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1838, \"entities\": []}]}"